{
  "texts": [
    "His cup-to-disc ratio was 0.05 RE and 0.0 LE.",
    "There was a normal optic disc RE and moderately severe disc edema LE, with no hemorrhages, lipid, or cotton wool spots.",
    "Visual field testing showed an arcuate visual field defect RE and a subtle central scotoma and inferior constriction LE.",
    "OCT showed a lamellar macular hole RE and significant macular edema LE, without vitreopapillary or vitreomacular traction in either eye.",
    "U/L amiodaroneassociated toxic optic neuropathy 8."
  ]
}